<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='881278' id='t-881278'>Now that's the Good Country Index.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='883496' id='t-883496'>What's it there for?</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='884865' id='t-884865'>Well, it's there really because I want to try</span>
